Classes

document:BibliographicReference
a
rdfs:Class
rdfs:comment
All information, structured along certain composition rules, to identify a resource in any format (print, audiovisual, digital, etc.), published or unpublished. Used for example to refer from a part in a text expression to a part in another text expression.
rdfs:isDefinedBy
document:
rdfs:label
bibliographic reference (en)
bibliographische Referenz (de)
riferimenti bibliografici (it)
référence bibliographique (fr)
skos:note
There is not 1 canonical way to write a bibliographic reference
rdfs:seeAlso
https://products.abc-clio.com/ ODLIS/ odlis b.aspx
rdfs:subClassOf
text-structure:ContentStructure
